explanation: "During prolonged fasting/starvation (\u2265 3\u20135 days), the body adapts to conserve glucose. The brain, which normally depends on glucose, shifts to using ketone bodies as its primary energy source.\n<img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/075ab831-7f3e-46d8-b1d5-8613dda9e0d2.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
