text: "A 17-year-old tall male presents for a routine check-up. He has long limbs, arachnodactyly, hypermobile joints, a high-arched palate, and an increased arm span. Genetic testing reveals a defect in the FBN1 gene. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis?",
