explanation: "Inhibitor A is a competitive inhibitor, and Inhibitor B is a non-competitive inhibitor.\n<img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/ba39f01e-a91b-4ab1-b8aa-7b90c404e140.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
