text: "A researcher treats cultured human cells with a histone acetyltransferase (HAT) inhibitor and observes rapid epigenetic changes. Within minutes, there is reduced transcriptional activity and chromatin appears more compact. Which of the following molecular changes is most likely to be seen immediately?",
